"      Heulitt MJ, Farrington EA, O'Shea TM, et al, &ldquo;Double-Blind, Randomized, Controlled Trial of Papaverine-Containing Infusions to Prevent Failure of Arterial Catheters in Pediatric Patients,&rdquo;",
"      <i>",
"       Crit Care Med",
"      </i>",
"      , 1993, 21(6):825-9.",
